<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākābdē munibhūdharājagaṇitē nārāyaṇāryyātmajā bhaktyā yāca
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kayūdhakalpaviṭapiprōttuṁgaśā<unclear>khō</unclear>pamā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Āsūryyasthitidīpama
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁbujamukhī rātriṁdiviṁ dīpakaṁ khyātā kuppamasaṁjñayā guṇa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yutā bhīmēśvarāyādadāt <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣa 977 gunēṁṭa bhīmē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śvaradēvarakuṁ jakravartti trailōkyamalladēvara pradhāni nā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rāyaṇabhaṭlu kuṁtuṟu kupama peṭṭina Akhaṇḍava<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ttilōhapu divi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ya yokkaṁṭikiṁ gilāramana cāmabōyu veṁṭiyayu bādabōyu
<lb n="8"/>doḍdiyaya nāvabōla bhīmayayuṁ gommabōla kāṭiyaya bera
<lb n="9" break="no"/>sina bōla vasa<unclear>mu</unclear>na niccina Eḍlu 50 ki nityapaḍi trabhu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vanāṁkuśamunaṁ bōyaṁgala nē mā 1 likhitaṁ bētanācāryya <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

